Class ZipDirectoryPath

java.lang.Object
  com.github.wuic.path.core.SimplePath
      com.github.wuic.path.AbstractDirectoryPath
          com.github.wuic.path.core.ZipDirectoryPath
All Implemented Interfaces:
DirectoryPath, Path
Direct Known Subclasses:
ZipEntryDirectoryPath, ZipFilePath
public abstract class ZipDirectoryPath
extends AbstractDirectoryPath
implements DirectoryPath

This class represents DirectoryPath for ZIP archives. Subclasses simply need to implement a getZipFile() method to retrieve a ZIP archive and absoluteEntryOf(String) method which returns an absolute path of a specified entry in the archive.
